    "The ISIC 2019 dataset is divided into the ratio of 70:20:10.",
    "The 70% of images are used for training, 20% for testing and 10% for validation.",
    "Multiple DL model hyper-parameters were utilized to train the suggested DVFNet architecture.",
    "The total trainable parameters employed by the DVFNet is 1,126,439.",
    "Using a 0.001 learning rate, a batch size of 32 and 40 epochs were used with the RMSprop optimizer."
